#: GatoGraphQLForWP/plugins/gatographql/src/ModuleResolvers/SchemaConfigurationFunctionalityModuleResolver.php:404
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Expose the <code>self</code> field in the GraphQL schema, which returns an "
"instance of the same object (for whichever type it is applied on), which can "
"be used to adapt the shape of the GraphQL response.<br/>%s<br/><span "
"class=\"more-info\">%s</span>"
